        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "Labor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme &quot;Asangathit Karmakar Samachar-Patr Hawker Cycle Sahayata Yojana&quot; for unorganized worker on 10 September 2010. Under this scheme, One cycle will be provided free of cost to each unorganized  beneficiary. The main objective of the scheme to empower the unorganized Samaachaar-Patr Hokar worker through provide them free cycle. \n",
        "benefits_md": "> A free of cost cycle will be provided. \n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
